The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves the use of information sets, which is a concept from information retrieval (cs.IR) and fuzzy sets (cs.LG). The use of non-overlapping windows to limit the number of features is a technique used in multimedia (cs.MM) and the comparison of the proposed method with other traditional methods involves machine learning (cs.AI).
